  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-26）：小米开源 MiMo-Embodied，赋能智能驾驶与机器人交互落地，重塑动态环境理解与推理能力",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500584&idx=1&sn=2d44ac22e2940f931a884afccdd482c4",
  "date": "2025-11-26 08:31:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MiMo-Embodied</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"178\" data-imgfileid=\"100016917\" data-ratio=\"0.15185185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1172\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b547a195&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXeXjib2iaiaJVrYzFXjaDF4ZySrxafteOxasKOfN2ZYicYqIrygDxZCiatEJ10zbAibicn4jBfKvq3tR2w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MiMo-Embodied 是小米推出的跨具身视觉语言基座模型，更是首个打通自动驾驶与具身 AI 两大核心领域的开源 VLM。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它以 70 亿参数实现了领域突破，在 17 项具身 AI 基准测试（涵盖任务规划、可用性预测等核心能力）和 12 项自动驾驶基准测试（含环境感知、驾驶规划等关键场景）中，性能显著超越同类开源与闭源模型。同时它还保留并强化了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">通用视觉理解能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，在动态物理环境中的理解与推理表现亮眼，为自动驾驶落地、智能机器人交互等场景提供了强大的技术支撑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mimo-embodied\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mimo-embodied</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：HunyuanOCR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"836\" data-imgfileid=\"100016918\" data-ratio=\"0.7166666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b7e381d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXeXjib2iaiaJVrYzFXjaDF4Z2GL6HvkOfAkjK7hBRCeTV0s2dQAKwMIyZ7vCf69AR7oHUwJ5OCGRew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">★</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">HunyuanOCR是一个领先的端到端OCR专家系统，基于Hunyuan的原生多模态架构。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型设计轻量，仅有10亿参数，但在多个行业基准测试中达到了最先进的水平。它在复杂的多语言文档解析中表现出色，并在文本识别、开放领域信息提取、视频字幕提取和照片翻译等实际应用中表现优异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuanocr\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuanocr</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Uni-MoE</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4759259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" data-height=\"556\" data-imgfileid=\"100016920\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7a83a05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXeXjib2iaiaJVrYzFXjaDF4Zt0W6dfcNiae1qXJFicosyEI1IavAS1D1JuJibIDNxDf4WFnfVUysQfbibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Uni-MoE是一个基于MoE（专家混合）架构的全模态大型模型，能够理解和生成多种模态内容。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目的最新版本Uni-MoE-2.0-Omni在语言为中心的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态理解、推理和生成能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">上取得了显著进步，支持跨十多种模态的交互，如图像、文本和语音。其动态MoE架构和渐进式训练策略使其在多模态任务中表现出色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uni-moe\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uni-moe</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：LLaDA2.0-flash</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"608\" data-imgfileid=\"100016919\" data-ratio=\"0.5212962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73097a72&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXeXjib2iaiaJVrYzFXjaDF4ZCkXfhZ4VjldkLPSfticmlFZAfyusx1Mo6gcVzK7xSa4UhVpfu5GIvkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LLaDA2.0-flash 是一种扩散语言模型，采用100BA6B混合专家（MoE）架构。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">作为LLaDA2.0系列的增强版，经过指令调优，优化用于实际应用。该模型在代码生成和复杂数学推理等任务中表现出色，支持工具调用，并在复杂的基于代理的任务中取得了优异的表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llada2-0-flash\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llada2-0-flash</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LeMiCa</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35555555555555557\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1170\" data-height=\"416\" data-imgfileid=\"100016921\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=081d69fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXeXjib2iaiaJVrYzFXjaDF4ZblwNNddo1ciaJ62xuMdTcYm7B7AiaDYIOHsLZQIFt91Licuk64xN6YVOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LeMiCa是一个用于基于扩散的视频生成的无训练加速框架，并可扩展至图像生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与使用局部启发式阈值的方法不同，LeMiCa将缓存调度表述为具有错误加权边的全局路径优化问题，并引入了词典序极小极大策略以限制最坏情况下的全局误差。这种全局规划提高了推理速度和帧间一致性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lemica\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lemica</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：ROCK</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.36944444444444446\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1170\" data-height=\"432\" data-imgfileid=\"100016922\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d6f4014a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXeXjib2iaiaJVrYzFXjaDF4ZiaAvsQnoRHYBp2OCO71KSGI4KUyh1kSbFkdASSrpciaGms177gJyg5iaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ROCK是一个易于使用且可大规模扩展的环境管理框架，主要用于Agent强化学习环境。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它提供了构建、管理和调度强化学习环境的工具，适用于开发、测试和研究场景。ROCK采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">客户端-服务器架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，支持不同级别的隔离机制以确保环境的稳定运行，并通过SDK支持与各种强化学习训练框架的集成。ROCK不仅支持传统的沙盒管理功能，还兼容GEM协议，提供标准化的强化学习环境接口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rock\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rock</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章精选并介绍了小米 MiMo-Embodied 等六个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖具身 AI、自动驾驶、多模态模型、OCR、视频生成加速及 Agent 强化学习环境管理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章精选并介绍了小米 MiMo-Embodied 等六个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖具身 AI、自动驾驶、多模态模型、OCR、视频生成加速及 Agent 强化学习环境管理。",
  "summary": "本文以“今日开源”的形式，集中发布了六个最新的开源 AI 项目。其中，小米推出的 MiMo-Embodied 作为首个打通自动驾驶与具身 AI 领域的视觉语言基座模型，在多项基准测试中表现出色。同时，文章还介绍了腾讯的轻量级 OCR 专家系统 HunyuanOCR、基于 MoE 架构的全模态大模型 Uni-MoE、指令调优的扩散语言模型 LLaDA2.0-flash、无训练视频生成加速框架 LeMiCa 以及 Agent 强化学习环境管理框架 ROCK。这些项目覆盖了当前 AI 领域的热点方向，为开发者提供了丰富的工具和模型选择，有助于推动相关技术在实际场景中的落地应用。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "小米 MiMo-Embodied 模型在具身 AI 与自动驾驶领域实现跨领域突破",
      "explanation": "MiMo-Embodied 是首个结合自动驾驶与具身 AI 的开源视觉语言基座模型，其 70 亿参数在多项基准测试中超越同类模型，为两大核心领域落地提供强大支撑。"
    },
    {
      "point": "多模态与 MoE 架构成为 AI 模型发展的重要趋势",
